v10218	01.09.2023	New Release using CUDA 12.0. Supported CC 5.0 - 9.0. Add few improvements. Removed use of 'textures'. Add application name and version. 
					Note: Linux application has to be built using GCC 12.2.1-4. Initiall try using GCC 13.0.1-6 was not succsessfull. It turns out CUDAv12.xx has issues
					with the GCC 13 (https://forums.developer.nvidia.com/t/identifier-float32-is-undefined-etc-cuda-12-2-0-gcc-13-1/258930). 